Actress Nkechi Blessing has stated she is not giving up hope on love. She said she is not averse to giving love another try. According to her, irrespective of the unpalatable experiences she has encountered, there is still a ray of hope shining in her as regards love.   ‘Stefflon the best woman Burna Boy will ever…     Actress Mercy Aigbe gives husband head cut     I want a private wedding – Temi Otedola   She said her experiences have not influenced her against negatively and she will not not talk down on people who have found love. Knowing that it might sound as though she has found love again, the actress assures fans not to worry about her as she is doing alright, she said: “Regardless of what I’ve been through in relationships. I Will never advise anyone against finding and falling in love. “Love is a beautiful thing and I am never ashamed of falling in love again. Don’t worry about me. I’m good.”